OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAnother hot day, dry and
OL,6,Fpredominantly sunny to end the week.
OL,7,FFeeling hot in many places with cooler
OL,8,Fconditions along coastal areas, with
OL,9,Fan onshore breeze.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FBecoming cloudy overnight
OL,12,Fwith low cloud and fog coming off the
OL,13,FNorth Sea and spreading slowly
OL,14,Fwestwards by the morning. Temperatures
OL,15,Fremaining warm overnight but cooler
OL,16,Falong the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
