OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FLow cloud and fog lingering
OL,6,Falong the coast but lifting inland and
OL,7,Fremaining cloudy for most. A moderate
OL,8,Feasterly wind will keep temperatures a
OL,9,Flot cooler than of late.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCloudy
OL,12,Fperiods throughout Sunday, though
OL,13,Fbrightening in the afternoon.
OL,14,FReturning to dry and largely sunny
OL,15,Fconditions by Monday. Tuesday sees low
OL,16,Fcloud and fog spread inland.
OL,17,FTemperatures around average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
